{"tid":1827863,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[手足勸世文] 自編自導論的禍害與成因","createTime":"2020-01-17T09:46:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-17T13:27:16.000Z","uid":123933,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"94e669628dfe87fce2684b436ac1aa16d5005ac9","tid":1827863,"uid":123933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T09:46:25.000Z","msg":"每次班狗一捉到有手足有武器，網絡上嘅輿論9成9都係話：「<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>做戲！老屈！砌生豬肉！</strong></span>咁易入口武器又唔見有狗死！」<br />\n<br />\n最後手足被補，還押，等候審訊。往往上庭時，公眾席係坐唔爆，又無人去送囚車。去到判刑時，呢班講做戲論嘅人又無晒聲出。<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>手足往往都成為condom。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n出現呢種輿論，原因有二：<br />\n一：人類鐘意乜都<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>陰謀論</strong></span>，放棄理性思考（我唔係話陰謀論係錯）。<br />\n二：武力接受程度低，<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>思想仍然未進入革命階段</strong></span></span>，與手足脫節。<br />\n<br />\n我係呢度懇求大家（我知好多人都無上連登，希望大家可以盡最大努力發放出去），請尊重手足，唔好再用做戲論去抵毀手足嘅一翻心機。<br />\n<br />\n手足要嘅，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>係支持，認同，與鼓勵，唔係要你地係咁講自編自導自演。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n請問下你自己，準備好革命未？<br />\n請問下你自己，咩叫核爆都唔割席？<br />\n請問下你自己，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>點解用你1-2個鐘，去聽審聲援要坐10年或更多嘅手足，都唔得？</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n有包伏，唔行得太前，兄弟爬山無問題！<br />\n但唔該，言行要一致，亦要與各手足同步心態。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">經歷咗咁多野，你仲覺得<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">推返暴政</span></span></strong>純粹靠堅守你嘅低武力原則係足夠嘛？</span><br />\n<br />\n希望各位香港人深思。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"color: orange;\">光復香港，時代革命。<br />\n香港獨立，唯一出路</span></ins></strong></span>"},{"pid":"63f1f5c43e7da6d08648a5e379a9a137f4fd520f","tid":1827863,"uid":123933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T09:47:31.000Z","msg":"隔離熱門po<br />\n話堅持自編自導論個位巴打<br />\n不服來辯<br />\n唔好一嚟就話人五毛分化撚"},{"pid":"6623904486e4afdc48a61797787e96d82aaadbe1","tid":1827863,"uid":123933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T09:49:05.000Z","msg":"革命不是請客食飯<br />\n手足有武器，我地應該加以支持同贊同，並唔係一嚟就話手足係被老屈。<br />\n<br />\n你地話老屈嘅，有無去過聽審聲援呢啲已經還押中嘅手足？有無寫過信俾佢地？"},{"pid":"8c2335ee8ec87f15d587bf8e0903971410c35427","tid":1827863,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T09:49:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">歐美議員講野又無人理啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日好多響task2呀 <br />\n幫手啦上唔到千呀</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Twitter組24小時keep住更新</strong></span><br />\n幫手retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=yrakYkBpMe8E3VCHF0kcypriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=b788999f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> /task2</span></strong></span> 攞任務"},{"pid":"fbc4d1735a16857e431a5653d6496c0fcd6e3d89","tid":1827863,"uid":123933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T09:49:52.000Z","msg":"說到底<br />\n請大家唔好再固步自封啦，提性自己武力接受程度。"},{"pid":"067e454611af7e2714e8c1599ef036becb899bf1","tid":1827863,"uid":123933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T09:50:09.000Z","msg":"希望大家可以廣傳。"},{"pid":"4befbfaf14f9bf21e7767e283525bdcbe8c2ece4","tid":1827863,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T09:51:22.000Z","msg":"放蛇機會好大其實<br />\n手足要買傳奇級玩具真係要好小心"},{"pid":"c33a828ff91db5aa88b3d05316c38eddf94ad1af","tid":1827863,"uid":123933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4befbfaf14f9bf21e7767e283525bdcbe8c2ece4","tid":1827863,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T09:51:22.000Z","msg":"放蛇機會好大其實<br />\n手足要買傳奇級玩具真係要好小心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T10:01:17.000Z","msg":"通常有四大原因：<br />\n1. 手足口疏<br />\n2. 有狗跟開<br />\n3. 放蛇<br />\n4. 有鬼"},{"pid":"16aeef51ab3096116a424374a40244d8ab215fc6","tid":1827863,"uid":123933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T10:01:38.000Z","msg":"你負皮我唔緊要<br />\n但可以同我辯論嗎？"},{"pid":"a2e2b7793b0faf18e6b2c584c9474a3366efb7bf","tid":1827863,"uid":123933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T10:20:13.000Z","msg":"有無人幫幫手"},{"pid":"f64ecbee5842ca796bc22afb673f065adbaa6b1f","tid":1827863,"uid":123933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T10:20:23.000Z","msg":"推下文"},{"pid":"8a185cbb80517d9015c43abd5bab6903796b7d0d","tid":1827863,"uid":123933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T10:35:36.000Z","msg":"P u s h"},{"pid":"4836293c3262a5fa957df1ee941d7fedfc99d28b","tid":1827863,"uid":123933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T10:47:27.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b36f6e0c54e18c15a153628a89f3b1c4176ea9b7","tid":1827863,"uid":123933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T12:26:51.000Z","msg":"p u s h"},{"pid":"59988a746d17e97aed1c5d7aefb9c8c73a165dc6","tid":1827863,"uid":123933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T12:27:01.000Z","msg":"p u s h"},{"pid":"0d59334c37a1c46a8288bc7f86bd19036fc83aef","tid":1827863,"uid":123933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T12:27:11.000Z","msg":"p u s h"},{"pid":"a8d9bb58896f749f0e0f837b453dbb621ac80581","tid":1827863,"uid":123933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T12:27:21.000Z","msg":"p u s h"},{"pid":"918afec74347ad0bdb350756d9558c9c0984d1b5","tid":1827863,"uid":123933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T12:27:31.000Z","msg":"p u s h"},{"pid":"98dbb117b0d1c4298b338e258397a2febb6b5dc8","tid":1827863,"uid":123